OL,3,CCalls for clarity over future of day
OL,4,Ccentres at risk of closure
OL,6,FOpposition councillors have called for
OL,7,Fclarity over the future of several day
OL,8,Fcentres that have been placed under
OL,9,Freview.
OL,11,FThe Reform-led Lancashire County
OL,12,FCouncil had been considering proposals
OL,13,Fto shut the five day centres after
OL,14,Fconcerns were raised about their
OL,15,F"significantly poor condition".
OL,17,FAlso included in the proposals, which
OL,18,Fwere the subject of a public
OL,19,Fconsultation, were potential plans to
OL,20,Fclose five care homes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
