OL,3,CCalls for clarity over future of day
OL,4,Ccentres at risk of closure
OL,6,FThe proposals were met with backlash
OL,7,Fand prompted protests from residents,
OL,8,Fworkers, and families. In January 2026
OL,9,Fthe County Council announced the five
OL,10,Fcare homes would not close, but a
OL,11,Fdecision has yet to be made on the
OL,12,Ffuture of the day centres.
OL,14,FConservative councillor Adam Brierley
OL,15,Fwelcomed the announcement, but said
OL,16,FLancashire County Council should
OL,17,Fprovide the "same assurance" to staff
OL,18,Fand users of the day centres.
OL,20,FHe said: "Residents, staff and
OL,21,Ffamilies can now sleep at night.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
