OL,3,CCalls for clarity over future of day
OL,4,Ccentres at risk of closure
OL,6,F"The county council has done the right
OL,7,Fthing with care homes ` now it needs
OL,8,Fto do the same for the day centres."
OL,10,FCllr Atkinson said they "had to bring
OL,11,Fforward" the announcement on the care
OL,12,Fhomes to stop "scaremongering" about
OL,13,Ftheir futures.
OL,15,FHe said: "The day centres are a
OL,16,Fdifferent thing to the home you live
OL,17,Fin ` it's a different magnitude of
OL,18,Fconcern.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
