OL,3,CCalls for clarity over future of day
OL,4,Ccentres at risk of closure
OL,6,F"There's been no decisions made on
OL,7,F(the day) centres. It will all come
OL,8,Fback...at the relevant time."
OL,10,FHowever, Cllr Brierley said that that
OL,11,Fstance was to underestimate the
OL,12,Fimportance of day centres to the
OL,13,Fpeople who rely on them ` and their
OL,14,Ffamilies.
OL,16,FHe said: "My message to Reform is that
OL,17,Fif they think the campaign has gone
OL,18,Faway, we're not going anywhere until
OL,19,Fthe day centres are also saved."
