OL,3,CCalls for clarity over future of day
OL,4,Ccentres at risk of closure
OL,6,FThe day centres being looked at are
OL,7,FByron View in Colne, The Derby Centre
OL,8,Fin Ormskirk, Milbanke Day Centre in
OL,9,FKirkham, Teal Close in Thornton
OL,10,FCleveleys and Vale View in Lancaster.
OL,12,FByron View and Teal House have already
OL,13,Fbeen shut for nearly six years, after
OL,14,Fclosing their doors ` and not yet
OL,15,Freopening them ` at the start of the
OL,16,Fpandemic in 2020. However, their
OL,17,Fclosures are still officially deemed
OL,18,Fonly as temporary ` and their
OL,19,Fpermanent status is subject to the
OL,20,Foutcome of the ongoing review.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
